{"about_the_game":"<img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2559860/extras/walk.gif?t=1723136528\" /><br><br>Three goblins have had enough of the intolerant society they are surrounded by. They have devised a brilliant plan to infiltrate sanctuaries of human indulgence, to fight for change<br>... by getting drunk.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2559860/extras/stairs.gif?t=1723136528\" /><br><br>Goblin legends tell of a beverage devised by ever-inventive humans, hidden away in their taprooms. They call it &quot;beer&quot;!<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2559860/extras/beer.gif?t=1723136528\" /><br><br>You must help these three goblins intrude on human festivities and snatch a mug of this legendary drink.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2559860/extras/library.gif?t=1723136528\" /><br><br>By controlling their delicate balance you will guide them through various pubs, markets, and banquet halls. Try not to blow their cover as they wobble through suspecting crowds, slippery tavern halls, and precarious castle walls. Utilize multiple routes through each level and open shortcuts by outsmarting various human contraptions and solving simple puzzles.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2559860/extras/door.gif?t=1723136528\" /><br><br>Be careful! Try not to fall and blow your disguise, as humans are suspicious creatures, and will kick you out of their town if they discover your dastardly plan.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2559860/extras/fall.gif?t=1723136528\" /><br><br>During your adventure, you will find many secrets and collectables. Such as those tasty-looking pretzels!<br><br>The game features:<br>- Multiple diverse locations, from village inns, backstreet alehouses, to castle halls<br>- Exciting! never-before-seen contraptions such as doors and levers<br>- Social stealth system<br>- Various hats and disguises<br>- Collectables<br>- In-Game Level Editor<br>- Free and unlockable cosmetics<br>... and lots of beer!<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2559860/extras/bridge.gif?t=1723136528\" />","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"First steps","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2559860/55841f6eaf7a6c6f8aa21902ea55b8bd520d0fd2.jpg"},{"name":"Party Starters","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2559860/702fed27d4162a63aadba9cecd5d35cdd5b18f11.jpg"},{"name":"Tavern Troublemakers","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2559860/dfb04e32b140c5ef8d62ed2a73a75454253c499f.jpg"},{"name":"Festival Fanatics","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2559860/f03d3775361407f5aa39228d08be5bdeb7f0e9e8.jpg"},{"name":"Keg Kings","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2559860/8e826f2e6ac92054d0064ff108a9b5edfc8604e3.jpg"},{"name":"Lookout's Lunch","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2559860/24cad4c56fe481ca02c8019d222acc0c837fad20.jpg"},{"name":"Terrace Treat","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2559860/71130749cbc3b1cd05af186feba535eb3480b756.jpg"},{"name":"Mystical Munch","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2559860/e4a264b0189ab8b1401845769690b20d470f3418.jpg"},{"name":"Trap Teaser","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2559860/377f0823367dd0e3952f3526ca338503bdb389ce.jpg"},{"name":"Sentry Snack","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/